276
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,880
And then form a big family

277
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,560
of mutual love and harmony.

278
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,080
I am willing to fight for it.

279
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,760
How do you want to fight?

280
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,160
I am willing to devote my life for my country.

281
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,880
Yannian, can you tell me,

282
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:19,520
what do you mean by devotion?

283
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,400
Devotion

284
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,320
means that I am always willing to sacrifice myself for my country.

285
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:26,880
How can you think of sacrifice at an early age?

286
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,960
Do you have to do this?

287
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:35,600
Uncle, I think in a country like ours,

288
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,920
there is no other way

289
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,160
to achieve this ideal.

290
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,800
I ask you,

291
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,360
what do you want to do

292
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,920
with your relationship with Liu Mei?

293
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,440
Actually, I have answered you

294
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,880
this question just now.

295
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,360
You answered me just now??

296
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:06,480
Then you have to forgive your uncle Liu's stupidity.

297
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,240
I really don't understand.

298
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:10,800
I told you just now.

299
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:12,800
I'm willing to

300
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:16,080
to dedicate my life for this country and its people.

301
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,480
So I have no intention of starting a family.

302
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,120
As a follower of anarchism,

303
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:23,040
I don't advocate starting a family.

304
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,040
As an anarcho-communist,

305
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:27,280
I abide by the six No's.

306
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,200
No falling in love. No personal relationships

307
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,560
is also the proper meaning of it.

308
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,240
Yannian.

309
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:41,760
There are many people advocating anarchism in China.

310
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,520
But which one is not married?

311
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,880
Which one doesn't fall in love?

312
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,520
Why do you want to go to this extreme?

313
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:51,120
You know, Liu Mei, in order to follow you,

314
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:53,920
she abandoned everything.

315
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,920
Do you think

316
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,520
you can afford to do this to her?

317
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,280
Uncle.

318
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,640
I know you came to see me about Liu Mei.

319
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,520
So I must answer you honestly.

320
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,640
I do so

321
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:11,360
also for Liu Mei's happiness.

322
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:12,640
I do so

323
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,560
also from our family after so many years of lessons learned

324
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,440
to make this decision.

325
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,920
How do you say this?

326
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,520
My father, Chen Duxiu,

327
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,600
was a man of great ideals,

328
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,000
a revolutionary who wants to have a family.

329
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:25,760
But I think,

330
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,920
in our disaster-stricken country,

331
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,920
it's impossible to do both.

332
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,880
I can't repeat the same mistakes.

333
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,920
Your heart is here.

334
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:50,960
Uncle, didn't you just ask me about my ambition?

335
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,200
I can give you a definite answer now.

336
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,800
From small rural areas to cities,

337
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,120
I personally felt

338
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,760
the corruption in this country and suffering of the people.

339
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,360
I'm now determined

340
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:05,200
to sacrifice everything for the strength of the country

341
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,720
and the happiness of the people.

342
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,920
I can't do it both ways like some people do.

343
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,080
So I have to sacrifice myself

344
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:13,680
without hesitation.

345
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,320
I see.

346
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:20,960
Sit down.

347
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:30,080
As an elder, I admire your ambition very much.

348
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,520
And I also firmly believe that

349
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:34,800
you will have an extraordinary life.

350
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:38,480
You and your father are made of special materials.

351
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:39,920
I'm not.

352
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,760
Liu Mei is my daughter.

353
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,720
I am responsible for her life.

354
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:47,280
Do you understand me when I say this?

355
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,200
Understood.

356
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:53,120
So I don't agree

357
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:56,000
with her going to France for work-study with you.

358
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,320
She doesn't need work-study now.

359
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:02,080
Now she needs to be in a famous foreign university

360
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,400
and study peacefully.

361
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,400
Please forgive me.

362
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:09,600
There's nothing I can do.

363
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:21,920
Uncle.

364
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,800
Then what else do I need to do?

365
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,880
What you need to do now

366
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:29,280
is do nothing.

367
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,920
Everything goes with the flow.

368
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,080
Don't hate me either.

369
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:03,600
Good.

370
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,040
Come a little closer

371
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,760
Help him with it.

372
00:17:09,120 --> 00:17:09,280
Good.

373
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:10,960
Look at the camera.

374
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:11,520
Good.

375
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:14,160
Lift a bit of the bride's veil.

376
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,840
I'll do it.

377
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:17,440
Good. Good.

378
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:21,120
Yannian, about my dad talking to you,

379
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,480
he told me everything.

380
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:25,600
And I know what you think,

381
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,600
I can't accompany you to France.

382
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:40,000
I don't know why recently.

383
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,320
Memories keep appearing in my mind

384
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,600
one after another.

385
00:17:48,320 --> 00:17:49,680
Remember the first time we met?

386
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,360
At the Aurora School.

387
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:52,640
We had a fight.

388
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:58,560
It has been more than four years now.

389
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:01,760
We went from Shanghai to Beijing.

390
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:03,280
From Beijing to Shanghai.

391
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,480
I remember we had a frugal canteen together.

392
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:08,800
Feeding the lambs together.

393
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:10,080
Making baozi together.

394
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,760
We made live dramas together.

395
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,720
Defeating Wang Jingxuan.

396
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,760
We made puppets together.

397
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:22,320
Going to prison, handing out leaflets, going to the streets.

398
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,040
I remember everything.

399
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:39,360
How I want to stay in yesterday!

400
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:42,000
But time can't stop.

401
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,040
I wish I didn't want to be here today.

402
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,680
But it's still here today.

403
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:51,280
Yannian, do you remember what I told you?

404
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:53,280
How much I admire you!

405
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:56,720
You can fly proudly and fly freely,

406
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,920
not relying on family.

407
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:00,560
I wanted to fly with you.

408
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:02,640
But today I found out,

409
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,280
I can't fly high.

410
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:08,000
I can't fly out either.

411
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,120
I made a detour.

412
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,640
I went back to this cage.

413
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:18,800
Do you remember what I told you?

414
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,600
Those three words are not in my dictionary.

415
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:24,240
But you're going to France soon.

416
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:26,000
I can't go with you.

417
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:30,000
I want to say, I'm sorry.

418
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,560
I get it.

419
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:38,240
I'm ugly, I'm stupid.

420
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:41,120
I can't do anything you ask me to do well.

421
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,200
But there is one thing,

422
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,360
I know I can't lie to myself

423
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:47,920
that I am always

424
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:52,320
thinking about you.

425
00:19:55,280 --> 00:19:56,640
I just want to ask,

426
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,920
on the road of your future life,

427
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,480
am I on it?

428
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:30,000
Okay.

429
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:36,720
I see.

430
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:39,120
You're going to France.

431
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,880
I can't see you off.

432
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:44,560
Take care of yourself and have a safe trip.

433
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:48,800
I'm leaving.

434
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:22,560
"Time flows like water,"

435
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:28,000
"Soon we shall depart from school,"

436
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:31,760
"We will ponder for a while"

437
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:35,600
"to understand today's homework,"

438
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:39,360
"Have we ever gone"

439
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:44,560
"against our teacher?"

440
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:48,320
"Parents want children to come home,"

441
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:51,760
"We should not wander on the road"

442
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:55,680
"of leading the country's future"

443
00:21:56,320 --> 00:22:00,320
"which depends on our generation,"

444
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,480
"Everybody, work hard!"

445
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:07,360
"Everybody, work hard!"

446
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,640
"Classmates!"

447
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:09,840
"Classmates!"

448
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:13,760
See you tomorrow.

449
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:02,240
I'm sorry.

450
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,960
Students, put the boxes in the car first.

451
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:15,520
Put it here first, put it here first.

452
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:16,800
Move someone else's first, move someone else's first.

453
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,080
Our luggage goes last.

454
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:18,880
Slow down!

455
00:23:19,360 --> 00:23:20,640
Here. Let me help you with your suitcase.

456
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,440
The boys help the girls move.

457
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:24,960
Put this on that.

458
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:25,840
Yannian.

459
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:27,440
Qiaonian.

460
00:23:27,520 --> 00:23:29,200
Put all the luggage in the front.

461
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:30,960
Here. Here.

462
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:31,680
I help you.

463
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,280
Thank you, so heavy!

464
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:34,880
Everybody, put your luggage in the front.

465
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,280
Okay.

466
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:38,800
Students quickly put their luggage on the bus.

467
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:39,840
Qiaonian.

468
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,240
Sister, I'll do it. I'll do it.

469
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:44,160
Pack the big luggages in the car.

470
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,080
Slow down!

471
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:46,400
Slow down!

472
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:46,960
It's really heavy.

473
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:51,840
Your family didn't come.

474
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,840
I didn't tell them. I don't think they know.

475
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,240
Come, sister.

476
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:01,360
Give it to me.

477
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:08,080
Sideways. Slow down.

478
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:23,280
Dad.

479
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:24,800
Dad.

480
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,120
Auntie didn't come.

481
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:32,640
She didn't. Your auntie is in Beijing.

482
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:36,560
Not coming is good. Better than crying.

483
00:24:38,560 --> 00:24:40,240
She asked me to bring you something.

484
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:42,720
Bring what?

485
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,040
Look at it on the ship.

486
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,960
Fried pumpkin seeds. Fried by me.

487
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:50,800
It's a mess.

488
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:04,640
It's a mess. It's your style of frying.

489
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,000
I'm in a bad mood.

490
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:12,160
Come on, this is enough for you to eat in France.

491
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:13,360
Come on.

492
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,920
You take this.

493
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:20,960
Take this, take this.

494
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:21,360
It's ok.

495
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,320
Give me this.

496
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:52,080
Come on.

497
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,120
Is everyone here?

498
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:56,880
Time's up.

499
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,160
It's time for us to start.

500
00:28:12,947 --> 00:28:18,947
