503
00:30:53,464 --> 00:31:06,685
[Chen Qiaonian, Member of the 5th Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, revolutionary martyr. Killed by the Kuomintang in Longhua, Shanghai in 1928, aged 26.]

504
00:32:22,834 --> 00:32:29,406
[2 Old Yuyangli, Shanghai French Concession]

505
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,280
Recalling the past?

506
00:33:28,320 --> 00:33:31,840
The former residence of Bo Wenwei of the Hunan-Anhui Comrades Association.

507
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,760
Vigorous.

508
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:36,240
No one here knows you better than you.

509
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:39,680
Years of greatness, mountains and rivers remain.

510
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,000
It's hard to be calm.

511
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:47,760
Brother Xingyan, I would like to thank you for saving me.

512
00:33:47,915 --> 00:33:50,183
[Zhang Shizhao, styled Xingyan]

513
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:50,240
Otherwise, I would still be in the prison.

514
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,720
Zhongfu, why should we thank each other?

515
00:33:58,080 --> 00:33:58,640
Sit.

516
00:34:08,080 --> 00:34:10,240
Zhongfu, I've already let the word out.

517
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:14,400
I, Zhang Shizhao, am willing to be Chen Duxiu's

518
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:17,920
defense attorney for life, for free.

519
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:19,120
I'm afraid, later on,

520
00:34:19,200 --> 00:34:20,880
there are many places where you'll need me.

521
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,080
What do you mean?

522
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:24,960
Defense attorney for life, for free.

523
00:34:25,680 --> 00:34:27,120
There are many places where I'll need you.

524
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:29,120
You mean I may have to go back to prison?

525
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:30,880
A slip of the tongue.

526
00:34:34,569 --> 00:34:35,717
No, no, no!

527
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:38,720
You don't have to bah.

528
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:40,800
Maybe your prophecy will come true.

529
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:43,200
No. In the future, I'll

530
00:34:44,160 --> 00:34:46,960
be in and out of the lab many times.

531
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:52,160
I hear you now have an obvious tendency

532
00:34:52,240 --> 00:34:54,000
towards Marx and the Russian revolution.

533
00:34:55,680 --> 00:34:56,960
Is it right to transform China

534
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,000
by having a new set of views?

535
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:00,000
I'm still exploring.

536
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:01,680
The Road of October Revolution

537
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,440
really inspired me a lot.

538
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:05,920
President Meng of Wuhan Cultural College

539
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,840
has heard a lot about you, Chen Duxiu.

540
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:11,600
He has asked me many times to invite you to give lectures in Hankou.

541
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,920
Look, you just got out of prison.

542
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,440
It's hard to get out again.

543
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,840
Why don't you lecture, like in the past?

544
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:22,560
Yes, I'd like to go.

545
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,120
What a happy promise!

546
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:28,000
Okay, I'll tell you the next thing.

547
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:29,840
About Southwest University.

548
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:32,480
After Mr. Sun Yat-sen founded the Kuomintang,

549
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:35,120
the Guangdong government strongly advocates ideological and cultural education.

550
00:35:36,080 --> 00:35:38,960
This allowed Chen Jiongming's proposal to establish Southwest University,

551
00:35:39,040 --> 00:35:41,440
which had been in the works for years, to pass.

552
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:43,120
The military government also dedicated

553
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:45,040
one million yuan for the preparation.

554
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,800
This Chen Jiongming adores you

555
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:51,440
and wants to poach you to go to Guangdong to run his education.

556
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,360
So he let me send you a telegram

557
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:55,360
and ask you to come here to talk about it.

558
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,200
He is afraid that you will change.

559
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,920
and asked me to bring a retainer fee, and letter of appointment.

560
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,520
Otherwise,

561
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:10,560
let's go in and hold an engagement ceremony.

562
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,680
You don't even ask me if I want

563
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:14,480
to do this.

564
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:15,440
You--

565
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:18,160
You don't want to? Why did come to Shanghai?

566
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:20,000
And I also know that

567
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,440
you sneaked out.

568
00:36:24,036 --> 00:36:26,230
[9 Jiangan Hutong, Beijing]

569
00:36:33,120 --> 00:36:33,760
Coming.

570
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:44,480
Hello, madam.

571
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,080
Is the gentleman at home?

572
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:47,200
No.

573
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:49,120
At the invitation of Mr. Zhang Tuzhao,

574
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:51,120
he went to Shanghai on business and hasn't come back yet.

575
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:55,040
I have been ordered to say hello to your husband.

576
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:56,240
Nothing else.

577
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:57,520
Excuse me.

578
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,320
Good bye.

579
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:01,120
Madam, leaving now.

580
00:37:37,378 --> 00:37:39,872
[Wuhan Cultural University Auditorium]

581
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,040
Fellow students.

582
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:51,040
For more than half a year,

583
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,480
the biggest change in China

584
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:58,560
is that people's wisdom is flourishing, people's spirit is flourishing,

585
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,400
the people have stood up,

586
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,920
putting forward the requirements of transforming society.

587
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:05,680
I personally think

588
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:08,800
this is the greatest achievement of the May Fourth Movement.

589
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:12,000
Hurrah!

590
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:18,240
What kind of requirements should social transformation meet?

591
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,320
Everyone is very concerned about this problem.

592
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:23,440
I spent 90 days in prison.

593
00:38:23,680 --> 00:38:25,440
I have some different ideas

594
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:27,120
about this problem.

595
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:30,000
Today, I will discuss with you

596
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,440
social transformation.

597
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:34,880
One, break the system of class,

598
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:37,280
to implement common people's socialism,

599
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,240
such that one should not have vanity.

600
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:43,680
Two, to abolish the system of succession,

601
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:46,880
we must practice common labor work

602
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:50,240
so that the proletarians do not suffer and the proletarians enjoy peace.

603
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:53,920
Three, to abolish the system of inheritance,

604
00:38:54,160 --> 00:38:57,280
land should not be passed down to private hands

605
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,920
and should belong to society as a whole.

606
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:04,000
People who don't farm should not have the right to the fields.

607
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:06,400
This is what Marx said.

608
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:08,800
To eliminate the system of private property.

609
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:11,040
Hurrah! Hurrah!

610
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:17,360
Such social transformation requires us to

611
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:20,160
establish two beliefs.

612
00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:23,440
That is, the belief in equality and the belief in labor.

613
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:25,440
Everyone should be educated

614
00:39:25,760 --> 00:39:26,880
and everyone should work often.

615
00:39:27,280 --> 00:39:30,320
Always in mind equal labor in your heart.

616
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:31,600
and labor revolution.

617
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:35,280
Today we talk about transforming society,

618
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,920
that is a fundamental transformation of society,

619
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,280
not improvement.

620
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,200
Fundamental transformation

621
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:43,120
means that, if necessary,

622
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:46,720
we must resort to bloody revolution.

623
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:50,240
Of course, we haven't reached

624
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:51,520
bloody revolution.

625
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:52,960
But we always have to have

626
00:39:53,040 --> 00:39:54,960
the means to study the revolution

627
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:57,600
and the faith to that time when the revolution is possible.

628
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:00,800
We must fight this devil!

629
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:05,920
Hurrah!

630
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:08,320
Hurrah!

631
00:40:09,600 --> 00:40:10,160
Hurrah!

632
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:13,840
Mr. Chen.

633
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,200
Come.

634
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:15,920
What's going on?

635
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:18,720
Mr. Chen, something happened.

636
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:20,800
We have caused you trouble.

637
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,880
What's the trouble?

638
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:27,520
The Wuhan authorities heard that Mr. Chen's

639
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,680
talk is about socialist ideas.

640
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:30,880
They're appalled.

641
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,800
A circular has been issued.

642
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:34,720
Mr. Chen is forbidden to speak

643
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:37,040
and you will be expelled from Wuhan.

644
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,520
I came to tell you.

645
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:42,240
Please try to leave Wuhan as soon as possible.

646
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,360
Save yourself from being killed.

647
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:48,320
I'm Chen. I'm a scholar.

648
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:50,720
It's been a great honor.

649
00:40:51,840 --> 00:41:01,120
Support Chen Duxiu!

650
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,360
When will Mom come back?

651
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,720
It's been a long time.

652
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,560
Dad will be back soon.

653
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:09,200
Dad will bring you delicious food when he comes back.

654
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:11,200
Do you miss your father?

655
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,200
Of course I miss him.

656
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:14,640
Mom misses Dad, too.

657
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,160
Dad!

658
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:19,120
Dad!

659
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,760
How can you speak of the devil?

660
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:24,160
What delicious food did you bring me, Dad?

661
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:25,520
Sesame candy.

662
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:28,160
How's it going? Have you seen Yannian and them?

663
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:30,320
Hurry up and slow down.

664
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,920
Finally, they met before they set off.

665
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:33,280
That's good.

666
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:34,880
Come. Come inside.

667
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,280
Brother Zhongfu is at home, right?
